  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103170/extras/04a1cea93f283e19c57fa73f8a470fd2.webp?t=1741358149\" width=616 height=50 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103170/extras/080260566b2841162e7c6dc5d424a77e.poster.avif?t=1741358149\" width=616 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103170/extras/080260566b2841162e7c6dc5d424a77e.webm?t=1741358149\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103170/extras/080260566b2841162e7c6dc5d424a77e.mp4?t=1741358149\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Luna's Twilight is a full-animation romance fantasy visual novel.<br><br>In a remote mansion, deep within a silent forest, four men from different races whisper words of love to you.<br><br>Among them, who will find a place in your heart?<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103170/extras/b24c22453dae74e3429ef2c11d6fcc46.webp?t=1741358149\" width=616 height=50 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103170/extras/cc0ed77c3225acc7e7296d42cb62087d.poster.avif?t=1741358149\" width=616 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103170/extras/cc0ed77c3225acc7e7296d42cb62087d.webm?t=1741358149\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103170/extras/cc0ed77c3225acc7e7296d42cb62087d.mp4?t=1741358149\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><table><tr><td><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103170/extras/52f89c29751958c07cf8f2d74bf53e4c.avif?t=1741358149\" width=74 height=74 /></span></td><td><strong>Shade</strong><br>A proud and arrogant young noble on the surface, but deep down, he's a simple, childish boy at heart.<br>His charisma and confidence are evident in his expressions and every move he makes.</td></tr><tr><td><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103170/extras/f64edb9f09e44a915b344cee229a32eb.avif?t=1741358149\" width=74 height=74 /></span></td><td><strong>Al Feouz</strong><br>A small, endearing boy with big, round eyes.<br>His insatiable curiosity keeps him buried in books, making him innocent and a bit shy.</td></tr><tr><td><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103170/extras/929158f9f9e36f768c7f7bc372899f8c.avif?t=1741358149\" width=74 height=74 /></span></td><td><strong>Raul</strong><br>A warewolf raised in the depths of the forest.<br>Honest and straightforward, though he has a hard time expressing his emotions.</td></tr><tr><td><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103170/extras/cb3fd67ea24cd16657f5cbff79bc9772.avif?t=1741358149\" width=74 height=74 /></span></td><td><strong>Tyrineon</strong><br>A beautiful elf with a gentle and kind demeanor.<br>Behind his ever-present smile, however, lies a sharp tongue that spares no one.</td></tr></table><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103170/extras/a99876750f8d6a60a2a56bfb0553a832.webp?t=1741358149\" width=616 height=50 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Character-Specific Routes</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103170/extras/406e78fafa457fe13daecf9ef364bbac.poster.avif?t=1741358149\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103170/extras/406e78fafa457fe13daecf9ef364bbac.webm?t=1741358149\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103170/extras/406e78fafa457fe13daecf9ef364bbac.mp4?t=1741358149\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Each of the four characters has their own unique story path. After the prologue, you’ll enter the route of your chosen character and follow their personal story until the very end. Each character is the true star of their own journey.<br>　<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Multiple Endings Based on Affection</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103170/extras/8ceaf3614251c786333137a83a824f0c.poster.avif?t=1741358149\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103170/extras/8ceaf3614251c786333137a83a824f0c.webm?t=1741358149\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103170/extras/8ceaf3614251c786333137a83a824f0c.mp4?t=1741358149\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Luna's Twilight doesn't have game overs. Instead, every choice you make influences the character's affection level. With three endings for each character and 12 total, what kind of ending will you uncover? What fate awaits you at the end of your journey?<br>　<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Immersive Animation in a Visual Novel</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103170/extras/f22da6324c210720d0a3328f240f01fd.poster.avif?t=1741358149\" width=616 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103170/extras/f22da6324c210720d0a3328f240f01fd.webm?t=1741358149\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103170/extras/f22da6324c210720d0a3328f240f01fd.mp4?t=1741358149\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The smooth animations create an immersive experience, making each scene feel vibrant and dynamic. Enjoy the beautifully animated CGs throughout the game and try to collect them all.<br>　<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3103170/extras/bac4c11457381dfb3da2f6055e0d4737.avif?t=1741358149\" width=616 height=220 /></span><br><br>The four unique men are waiting just for you in Luna's Twilight.",
